      • validPath

        public static boolean validPath(String path)
        Check path validity.
        Parameters:
        path - The name.
        Returns:
        true iff all of the following conditions hold:
        • The path is not empty.
        • The path begins with a forward slash (U+002F)
        • The path is not equal to "/" (U+002F)
        • Each path component, separated by "/" (U+002F), is valid.
        See Also:
        validPathComponent(String)

      • validPathComponent

        public static boolean validPathComponent(String name)
        Check path component validity.
        Parameters:
        name - The name
        Returns:
        true iff all of the following conditions hold:
        • The name is not empty.
        • The name does not contain the string ".."
        • The name matches the pattern [[.-_][A-Z][a-z][0-9]]+
